.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, salsa, classical, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey, biathlon, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
5. the fan of r&b is the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | salsa         | pop   | r&b    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | volleyball | biathlon | climbing |

