.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, satire, crime, adventure
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, volleyball, tennis, weightlifting
1. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching musical movies and the person watching satire movies##7
2. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
3. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person watching musical movies##7
4. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | crime | adventure | musical    |
| Sport         | snowboarding | weightlifting   | tennis   | volleyball |

