2. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
3. the engineer is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the engineer##7
5. the lawyer is not to the right of the librarian##8
6. the librarian is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the lawyer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Job     | engineer | lawyer | librarian | police-officer     |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | sailing        | rowing          | biathlon |

