.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, trance, folk, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike
1. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of electronic and the person driving the ship##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person driving the helicopter is the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the fan of folk is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
7. the fan of electronic is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
8. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | hip-hop | folk | trance |
| Transport     | quad-bike | helicopter       | ship  | jet-ski    |

