.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, kale, watermelon, broccoli
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, traveling, cooking, rock-climbing
1. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person eating kale##8
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating watermelon is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
7. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | kale        | broccoli | watermelon      | pear    |
| Hobby   | dancing | cooking   | traveling | rock-climbing |

