 5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
 7. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the person watching sports movies##8
 9. the person watching satire movies is not to the left of the person eating artichoke##8
