.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, pumpkin, lemon, banana
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, woodworking, cooking, baking
1. the person eating lemon is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person eating lemon is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is the person eating banana##1
5. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
6. the person eating pumpkin is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person eating banana##2
7. the person eating lemon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
