.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, goat, guinea-pig, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, train, van
1. the owner of the lizard is not the person driving the train##6
2. the person driving the train is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
3. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the lizard##7
4. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
5. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
6. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
7. the owner of the goat is not to the left of the person driving the van##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | mouse  | lizard | goat  | guinea-pig  |
| Transport   | bus | quad-bike   | van | train |

