.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, pony, lizard, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the tram is not the owner of the fish##6
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
4. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the snowmobile##7
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
7. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the taxi and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | pony    | guinea-pig | fish | lizard |
| Transport   | tram | taxi      | bike     | snowmobile     |

 